dataList.content: Why don't you... yield? You're too injured to fight.
Please... tell me what you think.
Would Yoshihide have forfeited the battle by this point? Or do you think...
... she wouldn't have put herself in this situation to begin with...?
How many times do I have to remind you? Forget all the useless flourishing and just go for the heart! The heart!
I've given you plenty of demonstrations, haven't I?!
Are you really gonna make me watch those clowns mop the floor with you?!
Bloody hell, she sure is a gasbag. Tell 'er to shut up, won't you?
... I've always known that this day would come.
But I was hoping... to meet my end while dueling Yoshihide herself... someone who was supposed to study... me...
So that the next Textbook can...
... learn from my mistakes... and make appropriate corrections to its content...
Hey, wait—
Stab the heart in front of you! Stab that bastard's heart! Now!
I cut apples in half
Hngh... Stop...
This right here is why you still haven't graduated from being a Textbook, do you hear me?!
Some were hard some crumbly some were soft some sappy
Your breathing is growing irregular... I understand.
This place has a way of... driving people completely mad.
The sugary smell...
... makes me...
Looks like...
... you've finally been freed from your bundle of liability.
Well? Do you feel liberated now, as you've always wanted?
... What, are you saying Lucio died or something?
Had his heart stabbed right out of him.
Isn't this what you wanted? You got your heart.
... Fuck off... with your bullshit.
Hey, Lucio!
Don't you dare ignore me. Say something.
Lazy little shit! You haven't even done a quarter of what you're meant to do. Who said you could lie down there like you're done?!
... Mate, you... you alright?
Wha... what...
What the fuck have you done, vermin?!
Nngh...
You... disgusting little shit...!
Greg—!
